text.tspan: A target of this this article is a mind. The goal is not to copy a human-animal nature of mind
and formalize it, but make a program with a high complexity structure, which would apply in practice some of the
logical blocks of human-animal and animal mind in combination with efficient algorythms and data
structures in computer science. As a result of this work it is expected to get a flexible data structure, which

tspan.tspan: would be able to solve efficiently any sort of task especially tasks, which require more complex approach.

other through the agency of sockets. The program can be devided into 4 main blocks:
Readers, interpreters, memory, output. This trivial representation meant to simplify the actual
difficulty of the program, because in fact there arn't any exact borders between these classes,
it is more like four trees standing next to each other and their
branches are tightly intertwined, so as roots.
